OL,3,CHow easy is it for underage children
OL,4,Cto buy knives?
OL,6,FGranada Reports Political
OL,7,FCorrespondent Lise McNally looks at
OL,8,Fhow easy it is for underage children
OL,9,Fto buy knives.
OL,11,FGreater Manchester Police officers
OL,12,Ftook to the streets to put shops to
OL,13,Fthe test and see if they would sell
OL,14,Fpotentially deadly weapons to underage
OL,15,Fteenagers.
OL,17,FThis undercover work is part of
OL,18,FOperation Venture, a multi-year effort
OL,19,Fto tackle violence and knife crime.
