OL,3,CHow easy is it for underage children
OL,4,Cto buy knives?
OL,6,FIt saw two underage police cadets,
OL,7,Faged 13 and 14, sent into various
OL,8,Fshops across Rochdale to see if they
OL,9,Fwere able to illegally buy knives.
OL,11,FOne shop sold them a six inch blade
OL,12,Fand neither were asked for ID.
OL,14,F"He didn't even give us a look - he
OL,15,Fjust took the money, and let us go
OL,16,Fwith it. I'm still shocked, we
OL,17,Fshouldn't really be able to buy that."
