OL,3,CHow easy is it for underage children
OL,4,Cto buy knives?
OL,6,F"I didn't think I was going to get a
OL,7,Fknife today, but now I have I feel a
OL,8,Fbit anxious... all it takes is one kid
OL,9,Fto come in and buy that, and then just
OL,10,Fmurder people."
OL,12,FThe focus of the operation is to test
OL,13,Fwhether knives are being sold to those
OL,14,Funder the age of 18 and to promote the
OL,15,F'Challenge 25' scheme to the stores.
OL,17,FSergeant Paul Heap from Greater
OL,18,FManchester Police says: "They're in
OL,19,Fbusiness to sell items from the shop,
OL,20,FI don't think they're thinking what
OL,21,Fthese items could be used for."
