OL,3,CHow easy is it for underage children
OL,4,Cto buy knives?
OL,6,F"You can see for yourself, it must be
OL,7,Fa six inch blade there... it could
OL,8,Fkill someone without a doubt."
OL,10,F"That's why we're going down that
OL,11,Feducation and learning, making sure
OL,12,Fthey understand what the consequences
OL,13,Fcould be."
OL,15,FOf the six shops they visited, only
OL,16,Fone broke the rules. But the online
OL,17,Fmarketplace is much harder to police.
